Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/hasConcept
Object: Relates a concept annotation to a SKOS concept, being the subject of the thing being annotated. A SKOS concept may be referenced by one or more annotations, or none. An annotation always references one concept.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/TemporalThing
Object: An interval between two points in time, having a name.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/description
Object: Relates a thing to its textual description.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/Label
Object: Allows a thing to have different labels at different time periods. e.g. a Government Department, Select Committee, Bill or inquiry might change its name during its lifetime. Reuses preferredLabel, abbreviationLabel, sortLabel, startDate and endDate from Thing.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/Identifier
Object: An identifier from an external system. Might be another Parliament system or an external system such as Wikidata.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/isInterestDeclared
Object: Determines if an item of Member activity includes a declaration of interest by that Member, without describing the nature of the interest. The interest declared may or may not relate to an interest registered in the Register of Members' Financial Interests.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/abbreviationLabel
Object: Relates a thing to an abbreviation label.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/MemberActivityThing
Object: An item of Member activity, for example: a tabled question or a spoken contribution.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/createdAt
Object: Relates a thing to its date of creation.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/WebLinkType
Object: A link type e.g. personal homepage, obituary.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/proposedEndOn
Object: Relates a temporal thing to its proposed end date.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/identifierValue
Object: Relates an identifier to its value.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/ConceptAnnotation
Object: The annotation of a thing with a SKOS concept, used to refer to that thing in a subject index.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/hasIdentifier
Object: Relates a thing to an identifier.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/sortLabel
Object: Relates a thing to a sort label e.g. Churchill, Winston.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/hasWebLinkType
Object: Relates a link to a weblink type.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/Thing
Object: A thing. Anything. At all. Provides a set of properties for reuse by any other model.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/preferredLabel
Object: Relates a thing to its preferred label.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/hasConceptAnnotation
Object: Relates a thing to a annotation of that thing with a concept. A thing may have one or more concept annotations, or none. An annotation always annotates one thing.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/ordinality
Object: Relates a thing to its ordinality within a wider set of things.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/scheduledEndAt
Object: Relates a thing to its scheduled end time.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/hasIdentifierSource
Object: Relates an identifier to its source.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/hasWebLink
Object: Relates a thing to a web link. e.g. Person to a twitter account.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/includesRequestForStatistics
Object: Determines if an item of Member activity includes a request for statistical information.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/IdentifierSource
Object: An identifier source. The system or website from which the identifier originates.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/updatedAt
Object: Relates a thing to the date of its most recent update.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/WebLink
Object: A web link with a source, type and URL.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/sameAs
Object: Relates a thing to the same thing described elsewhere on the web. Initially intended for wikidata non-information resource URIs.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/endAt
Object: Relates a thing to its end time.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/url
Object: Relates a web link to a URL.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/
Object: Provides a set of common properties for reuse by other models.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/startAt
Object: Relates a thing to its start time.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/endOn
Object: Relates a thing to its end date.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/hasLabel
Object: Relates a thing to a label during a time period.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/proposedStartOn
Object: Relates a temporal thing to its proposed start date.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/startOn
Object: Relates a thing to its start date.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/scheduledStartAt
Object: Relates a thing to its scheduled start time.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/precededBy
Object: Relates a thing to its predecessor. Usually the thing and its preceding thing will be of the same class.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/hasWebLinkSource
Object: Relates a web link to a link source.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/utility/WebLinkSource
Object: The publisher of the URL identified by the web link e.g. The Daily Mail, personal website, Facebook, Wikipedia.
